CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 9, 1960, pg. A14, reads: "Scholarship Aides - This quintet of vivacious youth, anxiously anticipating results of their scholarship affair, include, first row, left to right: Anne L. Scott, chairman; Sylvia Ellison and Mary Stephens. Back row: Zilphia and Arlean Gantt. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, seated from left: Anne L. Scott, Sylvia Ellison holding card, Mary Stephens; standing: Zilphia Gantt and Arlean Gantt, posed in interior
